thread.title_full: TENAQUIP Limited reviewed by Scott Moorehead, Longliner Seafoods

author: Scott Moorehead, Longliner Seafoods
title: Scott Moorehead, Longliner Seafoods
text: Was unable to find our preferred brand of oilskin pants in the sizes and style we have used for many years anywhere in Vancouver. Found they were available online from TENAQUIP and after a quick phone call with their order desk , they were on there way ! Arrived as advertised and at a great price
